criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age ≥ 65 years;

          -  Frail institutionalized.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cognitive impairment;

          -  Fracture;

          -  Neurological disorder;

          -  Unable to follow verbal instructions;

          -  Score lower than 60 in the Barthel Index.
